  "description": [
    "Society News Senora de Odria Due In Capital Next Week Mrs Truman to Entertain at Lunch For Visitor Other Parties Set By Katharine M Brooks Mrs Truman will entertain at luncheon Tuesday October 21 in honor of Senora de Odria wife of the President of Peru Senora de Odria was here in the late sum mer and stayed at the embassy while the Ambassador and Senora de Berckemeyer were in Mexico for the International Bank meet ings After a short visit with them on their return the Peru vian Presidents wife went to Can ada where she isthe guest of the Peruvian Ambassador German Fernandez Concha and Senora de Fernandez Concha The Ambassa dor formerly was commercial coun selor at the Washington embassy and he and Senora de Fernandez Concha have many friends here They have given several small and informal parties for Senora de Odria in the Dominion capital President and Mrs Truman are entertaining old friends from Independence and nearby com munities Monday evening they had a small company of guests at dinner in honor of Judge and Mrs Emory Wright of Blue Springs Mo not far from Inde pendence and the Misses Eleanor and Grace Minor of"
